Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Big Five's Trap:\N Duel Monsters Quest"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting you guys weren't counting on me showing my face here again, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear you five aided Pegasus in his attempted take over of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Because of you jerks, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The act of treason you've committed isn't something that can be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As president of this company, I hereby fire every one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plain {\i1}sight{\i0} of you disgusts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We only did what we did because of your loss to Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-sama, we only agreed to work with Pegasus to save the company's reputation from plummeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We only acted on the best interest of our reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to save it, we have developed a new adventure game based off of Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventure game...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, president.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you play a little game with us, gambling on your firing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are to lose this game, we will humbly accept our loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are to win, you cannot fire us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're challenging me to a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Seto Kaiba, will accept {\i1}any{\i0} game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, why'd you go and accept?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply going to make sure they never {\i1}think{\i0} of trying to get their revenge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat them into next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And demonstrate my power over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please insert cards in Deck Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Setting position. Please sit patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Position locked. Beginning game. Standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother! This can't be good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fret it! Start it up, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Challenging me to {\i1}this{\i0} level of game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon-Type Sealing Jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...! Pull yourself together, big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with that, the president has been trapped within the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless you can win the game, Seto-sama's consciousness will forever remain trapped within the game's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, Kaiba Corporation now belongs to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba, allow us to take you hostage once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mokuba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Ain't that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You imbeciles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba will return to us in no time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that over-obsessive little brother would abandon Seto-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he may get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter {\i1}who{\i0} he gets to help him, the result of this game is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go! The new cards you ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun got trapped in the Adventure Game's world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean if he loses, he can't escape the game?! That's no game at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... My big brother... Please save my big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're up against the top executives of Kaiba Corporation. This is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother... Big brother's true dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is to build Kaiba Land around the world so kids all over can enjoy themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it... Kaiba had a dream like {\i1}that{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that my big brother put his life on the line for Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one realizes how much he puts his heart into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us are gonna just abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We're fully aware of how strong the bond between you two is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really grown into a reliable man, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba Corporation has been taken over by the Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then what'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe that the simulators at Kaiba Land have the same programming they used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. They're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got access.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So only three people can go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the {\i1}other{\i0} guy is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose the game, you won't be able to come back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no meaning for me in a world without my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That decides it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! You're on house duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys better return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kaiba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they left...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they came back, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he brought {\i1}that{\i0} Yugi Mutou with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to trap Yugi Mutou and his friends in the Game World at Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this world is related to Duel Monsters somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rules must we follow in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't feel like your ordinary graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've seen this terrain somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder Circus Zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Warrior Zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Monsters, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rude Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just have to order them to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Flame Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning Fighting Spirit Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your attack, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Swordsman just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their Attack Points increase whenever they revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, think back to when you fought Kotsuzuka back in the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be aware of what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to beat Zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies have 0 Defense Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate! Shield in the Right Hand, Sword in the Left Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Black Magician!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we got some gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This appears to be this world's currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Life Points didn't return!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when it reaches 0?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sprite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When sprites appear in a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's usually some kind of hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mokuba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really {\i1}eat{\i0} these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Rare Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy em!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,000 gold...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a card when we beat that Monster earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just {\i1}5{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, let's hurry up and look for my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some information!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, did you find anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~ Nothing at all~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They saw someone they didn't recognize being carried up to the Cave of Death located in those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the only way to get to the Cave of Death is to cross this desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds {\i1}easy{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-h-h-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back, Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... without big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sand storm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were blown all the way back to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't cross the desert like {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps! Ya know something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya plan on crossin' the desert, ya need the Cluck card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cluck"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the {\i1}card{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, do you know how we can get that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya plan on crossin' the desert, ya need the Cluck card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that a second ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ya plan on crossin' the desert, ya need the Cluck card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Keeps on sayin' the same thing...!\N-So if we don't get the Cluck card...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get out of this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's focus on finding out how to get the Cluck card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a way to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall {\i1}not{\i0} succeed in rescuing Seto Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, haven't they been gone for a while now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Yugi's a gaming genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way he could clear it that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all about the first crush I ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story of Hiroto Honda's First Ever Love Interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really wanna hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll tell you about my writing class' essay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Dream is to be a Pilot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know the situation we're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the enemy has infiltrated the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, let's make a barricade in front of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came up with nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took us so much effort to get to this town, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's come kind of computer bug...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go look again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Won't you challenge us for a shot at Champ?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The current prize for victory is the Cluck card."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So, your trial is waiting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"-The Ruler and Killer of Darkness"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youse gonna enter for a shot at Champ, gecko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Winnin' ain't no easy task, gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be alot of trouble fer us if we had a weakling as the Champ, gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty, yer fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sign you guys up, gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, here's the mask and mantle you gotta wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya just fight each other till one of yer Life hits 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until your Life reached 0...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone whose Life hits 0 can't return to the real world alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if your Life hits 0, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can easily win without {\i1}my{\i0} help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But without {\i1}you{\i0}, we can't clear the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long since we've had a challenger for our invincible Champ, has it not, gecko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we got a ferocious man comin' to challenge the Champ's position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wears a pig mask, and is unshaken by death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Piglet Warrior, Joe, gecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} gonna fight the Champ for her title!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell the Champ'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I got a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold out invincible Champ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Butterfly, gecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Champ's a {\i1}woman{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The identity of the warrior woman standing before Yugi and the others in the Coliseum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is none other than Mai Kujaku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Mai joining, Yugi and his party cross the desert to save Kaiba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they were able to make it to the Cave of Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't find Kaiba-kun, but a girl that looks {\i1}exactly{\i0} like Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and the guys are the chosen legendary heroes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "Duel Monsters Quest 2: The Legendary Hero, Yugi"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:21:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:22:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
